Oyster Genome, indexing etc. 

Genomic .fna , gff files were downloaded at ftp://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/genomes/all/GCF/000/297/895/GCF_000297895.1_oyster_v9
  C.gigas.fna
  C.gigas.gtf(3)

To supply a GTF file for hisat2_extract_exon/splice sites: 

$module load cufflinks. 
$gffread C.gigas.gff -g C.gigas.fna -T -o C.gigas.gtf (-T to output gtf file)
  No fasta index found for C.gigas.fna. Rebuilding, please wait..
  Fasta index rebuilt.
  
Output given: 
-- C.gigas.fna.fai
-- C.gigas.gtf
  
Splice/Exon sites:

$python /home/bdigby/bin/hisat2-2.1.0/hisat2_extract_splice_sites.py C.gigas.gtf > C.gigas_splice_sites.txt
$python /home/bdigby/bin/hisat2-2.1.0/hisat2_extract_exons.py C.gigas.gtf > C.gigas_exon_sites.txt

Building Genome index:

$HISAT2/hisat2-build --ss C.gigas_splice_sites.txt --exon C.gigas_exon_sites.txt -f C.gigas.fna C.gigas
--C.gigas.1.ht2
..
--C.gigas.8.ht2
